      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Good race with several win chances. LET'S DO IT AGAIN (2) has been going well, scoring a narrow win over WATERMELON two back then finishing a close-up fourth on the Gold Coast poly after drawing off the track. Much better draw this time and gets his chance to bounce back. EMPIRE OF ART (6) is also racing in great heart, finishing a close-up fourth at Doomben two back then runner-up at Ipswich. Overdue and expecting a bold showing again. WATERMELON (1) is a tough galloper going well and has five poly track wins. Placed only try at this course and distance and among the main hopes. INSIDE PASSAGE (4) is a progressive type who scored here last time and can make it back-to-back wins.",
